{"word":"G1311 - διαφθείρω - diaphtheírō - dee-af-thi'-ro - Corrupt","slug":"G1311","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαφθείρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diaphtheírō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-af-thi'-ro"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Corrupt"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03C6;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C9; - diaphtheiro&#x0304;</b> - <i>dee-af-thi'-ro</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5351\">G5351</a>; to <i>rot thoroughly</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>ruin</i> (passively <i>decay</i> utterly, figuratively <i>pervert</i>): - corrupt, destroy, perish."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1312\">G1312</a>, <a href=\"#/G2704\">G2704</a>, <a href=\"#/G5256\">G5256</a>, <a href=\"#/G5349\">G5349</a>, <a href=\"#/G5351\">G5351</a>, <a href=\"#/G861\">G861</a>, <a href=\"#/G862\">G862</a>, <a href=\"#/G90\">G90</a>"}]}